reviewText: The Footage Should've Been A Lot Better But Other Than That Have No Complaints

This is an excellent way for wrestling history buffs who want to see just what kind of product Don Owens was offering that kept the interest of Portland Wrestling fans for so long. It was great to see how Billy Jack Haynes got his start in the wrestling business that made him such a success in all the territories he traveled to. A must for the true wrestling fan,
video quality was bad like recorded from a VHS tape
Great DVD, great matches if one likes old school wrestling, fast shipping and product as advertised, STARS!!!!
the barry owen presents best of Portland wrestling vol1 thank you for all help.

Great Coverage of the Northwest, this is a great DVD with the history of the Portland Wrestling talent. They captured the time capsule of basic Pro wrestling coverage. Complete with great match ups, commentary, and how it truly was during the magic time in Pro Wrestling.
